channel.title: Stop trying to sell my source you fucking retards
channel.description: Stop trying to sell my source you fucking retards. Any money gained off it should go straight to me anyway for wasting 2 weeks of my life coding it. All you did was dl and once it was removed you think you're the only one with it. Whatever, just stop trying to profit off of other people work or else I'll re-release it for everyone to use. [center][img]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/Themes/default/images/warnmute.gif[/img] Releasing something only to withdraw the release is silly. Besides, once something enters the public domain it should stay that way. If you don't like people selling your toy (which staff cannot prevent if it isn't done on this website) then actually re-release it, rather than winging.[/center]
